    POS 0 200 -200
    DIFF 1.0 1.0 1.0   	//white light
    SPEC 1.0 1.0 1.0	//full  white specular

LIGHT
    POS 0 200 200
    DIFF 1.0 1.0 1.0   	//white light
    SPEC .5 .5 .5	//full  white specular



